android.car.annotation

注释类型 AddedIn

  • 已过时。 
    use ApiRequirements instead.

    @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={ANNOTATION_TYPE,FIELD,TYPE,METHOD})
 @Deprecated
public @interface AddedIn
    Tells in which version of car API this method / type / field was added.

    For items marked with this, the client need to make sure to check car API version using Car.API_VERSION_MAJOR_INT for major version and Car.API_VERSION_MINOR_INT for minor version.
